## 🎮 Using the App

### **Live Detection Tab**

1. Click **"Start Detection"** checkbox
2. Allow webcam access when prompted
3. See live video with pose landmarks
4. Watch posture score update in real-time

### **Posture Score**

- **75-100**: ✅ Good (Green)
- **50-74**: ⚠️ Fair (Orange)
- **0-49**: ❌ Poor (Red)

### **Fall Detection**

- When person bends significantly
- Audio alarm plays (3 beeps)
- Counter updates
- SMS alert (if configured)

### **Analytics Tab**

- Session statistics
- Total frames processed
- Falls detected count
- Processing status

